      "updated": 1618100912
    },
    {
      "id": "607242a6fd049e000076d6a3",
      "text": " [全角修正後全文（英語）の冒頭が読める魚拓 https://megalodon.jp/2019-0530-2156-19/https://www.asahi.com:443/articles/ASGBC3CJJGBCUHBI00K.html]",
      "userId": "5d20a16b6e57f80017fd049e",
